OL,5,CSAVE NORTH SEA FISH STOCKS R  #///'! +$
OL,7, European environment and fisheries     
OL,8, ministers met last week in Norway to   
OL,9, protect North Sea fish stocks.         
OL,11, With more thanC200 speciesGof fish,    
OL,12, the North Sea is one of the most       
OL,13, productive fisheries in the world.     
OL,15, But Jonathan Fulcher,Gof theCWorldwide 
OL,16,CFund for Nature,Gwarns:G"Most of those 
OL,17,Gstocks are at the point of collapse."  
