OL,4,B````````R,./B``````````````R&o|nw 
OL,5,CSAVE NORTH SEA FISH STOCKS R  #///'! +$
OL,7, At the lastCInternational Conference on
OL,8,Cthe Protection of the North SeaGin 1995
OL,9, environmental ministers agreed         
OL,10, over-fishing was an immediate problem. 
OL,12, "However despite that clarion call to  
OL,13, armsCnothing has been doneGto remedy   
OL,14, the problem," says Jonathan Fulcher    
OL,15, from the Worldwide Fund for Nature.    
OL,17, "Largely because lengthy and confusing 
OL,18,Cpolitical processes prevent action!"   
