OL,4,B````````R,./B``````````````R&o|nw 
OL,5,CSAVE NORTH SEA FISH STOCKS R  #///'! +$
OL,7, "European ministers should put         
OL,8,Cimmediate recovery plansGin place for  
OL,9, those North Sea stocks that are over-  
OL,10, fished," says Jonathan Fulcher from the
OL,11, Worldwide Fund for Nature.             
OL,13, "This may require the establishment of 
OL,14,Cmarine refuges,Gin order to rebuild    
OL,15,Gfish stocks.                           
OL,17, "In addition,Ccommercial fishingGshould
OL,18, be controlled stringently, otherwise   
OL,19, the North Sea faces depletion."        
