OL,4,B````````R,./B``````````````R&o|nw 
OL,5,CSAVE NORTH SEA FISH STOCKS R  #///'! +$
OL,7,CEnvironment secretary John GummerGwarns
OL,8, it is "vital to reach agreement as soon
OL,9, as possible on a new fishing strategy  
OL,10, for the North Sea."                    
OL,12, He says his aim is to protect fishing  
OL,13, stocks and to stop them being destroyed
OL,14, in the same way in as those on the     
OL,15,CGrand BanksGoff Canada.                
OL,17, He adds: "By protecting stocks we are  
OL,18, also protecting the long-termCinterests
OL,19,Cof fishermen."                         
