OL,4,B````````R,./B``````````````R&o|nw 
OL,5,CSAVE NORTH SEA FISH STOCKS R  #///'! +$
OL,7, Environment Secretary John Gummer says 
OL,8, any plan developed for the North Sea   
OL,9, could be used as a blueprint for       
OL,10,Cworldwide conservationGof fish stocks. 
OL,12, He says: "That means we must find an   
OL,13, answer in whichCfishermen join with    
OL,14,Cenvironmentalists and governmentsGto   
OL,15,Gto find a solution we can all stick to.
OL,17,C"SurveillanceGis essential, science is 
OL,18, essential and a means of getting all   
OL,19, fishermen to obey rules is imperative."
